The Game of Life kata is complete. I implemented:

- `src/game-of-life.ts` — sparse implementation using a `Map` of neighbor counts derived from living cells, applying Conway's rules (survive on 2-3 neighbors, birth on exactly 3).
- `src/game-of-life.spec.ts` — 10 tests covering empty grid, underpopulation, survival, birth, overpopulation, the 2x2 block still life, blinker oscillation, glider movement, and negative coordinates.

All 10 tests pass.
